title: The King is here
description: Danielle and superstar sub Matt McConkey are blessed and impressed to have iconic housewives producer (as well as many other shows) Carlos King is in the nook and his takes are hot! From literally being in the room where it happened during the infamous NJ table flip to being the Nene whisperer, this king has seen it all and lived to tell the tale. We talk Marlo's peach, new New York, and why Jennifer Aydin shouldn’t dish out what she can’t take. An insider takes us deeeeep inside and this episode is not to be missed.
